I wanted the Wedding Crashers and found this two movie set for the same price.  I had never seen the Wedding Singer before but it turned out to be a cute movie and worth watching and it was essentially free.
Great price for two excellent, funny movies. I highly recommend these movies .

For those interested, this Classic 00's Rewind double feature coming up April 26th, 2017 has both the rated AND unrated Uncorked editions of Wedding Crashers! The original release containing both cuts has been out of print for some time, so it's great to see New Line/Warner finally re-releasing it via this new double feature!
